(I've decided to take Rattrap.)


Rattrap:




Rattrap saw a handful of bots attacking the Arc. He could have done 
something about it, if someone was there to push him into something crazy 
like that, and if he wasn't damaged.

He slowly backed out, keeping his optics on the attacks. He ducked his body 
behind a boulder and made his way out of the area. He kept a look out for 
his own back, watching for Hell Beast's troops, even Megatron's.
